data.meta_description: Sylvester Dawson was born on January 15, 1823 in Lost Creek Harrison County West Virginia, Verenigde Staten, son of John Dawson and Susanna Swisher., they had 2 children. He died on September 24, 1896 in Lost Creek Harrison County West Virginia, Verenigde Staten. This information is part of My Giant Family Tree by Jennifer Swisher on Genealogy Online.
